Author: bruno_guy
Text: i feel like some picture make it look like she gained weight, but what i see the only difference is she looks more fuller like not fatter but just not as "boney" and i hate saying that because my mom is always saying that to me like "your starting to look boney and a lot of people dont think thats a healthy look. but at the same time i don't want to say she looks healthier because she was probably healthy back then just maybe now shes not depriving herself if that makes sense

Author: ArabellaDC
Text: I'm not saying Jessica looks huge, but compared to last year she gained around 20lbs a least, and she edits her photos a lot, but in the last video you can see how she looks in real life
